research-experiment-autopsy-human-name = Human Autopsy Experiment
research-experiment-autopsy-human-desc = We dont want to invest in a station that doesnt know their coccyx from their cochlea. Send us back data dissecting a human to receive more funding.
research-experiment-autopsy-nonhuman-name = Non-human Autopsy Experiment
research-experiment-autopsy-nonhuman-desc = When we asked for a tail bone, we didnt mean...look, just send us back data from something OTHER than a human. It could be a monkey for all we care, just send us research.
research-experiment-autopsy-xenomorph-name = Xenomorph Autopsy Experiment
research-experiment-autopsy-xenomorph-desc = Our understanding of the xenomorph only scratches the surface. Send us research from dissecting a xenomorph.
research-experiment-ordnance-explosive-highyieldbomb-name = High-Yield Explosives
research-experiment-ordnance-explosive-highyieldbomb-desc = Several reactions react very energetically and can be utilized for bigger explosives. Capture any tank explosion with a Doppler Array and publish the data in a paper. Any gas reaction is allowed.
research-experiment-ordnance-explosive-lowyieldbomb-name = Low-Yield Explosives
research-experiment-ordnance-explosive-lowyieldbomb-desc = Low-yield explosives may prove useful for our asset protection teams. Capture a small explosion with a Doppler Array and publish the data in a paper.
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-bz-name = BZ Gas Shells
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-bz-desc = The delivery of BZ gas into an area of operation might prove useful. Pack the specified gas into a tank and burst it using a Tank Compressor. Publish the data in a paper.
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-nitrous-oxide-name = Nitrous Oxide Gas Shells
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-nitrous-oxide-desc = The delivery of N2O into an area of operation might prove useful. Pack the specified gas into a tank and burst it using a Tank Compressor. Publish the data in a paper.
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-frezon-name = Frezon Gas Shells
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-frezon-desc = The delivery of Frezon gas into an area of operation might prove useful. Pack the specified gas into a tank and burst it using a Tank Compressor. Publish the data in a paper.
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-plasma-name = Plasma Gas Shells
research-experiment-ordnance-gaseous-plasma-desc = The delivery of Plasma gas into an area of operation might prove useful. Pack the specified gas into a tank and burst it using a Tank Compressor. Publish the data in a paper.
research-experiment-physical-arcade-winner-name = Playtesting Experiences
research-experiment-physical-arcade-winner-desc = How do they make these arcade games so fun? Lets play one and win it to find out.
research-experiment-scanning-cytology-slime-name = Vat-Grown Slime Scan
research-experiment-scanning-cytology-slime-desc = Seen the slimes in the xenobiology pens? They spawned when our researchers donked a moldy bread slice into the vat. Cultivate another one and report the results.
research-experiment-scanning-fish-name = Fish Scanning Experiment 1
research-experiment-scanning-fish-desc = An experiment requiring different fish species to be scanned to unlock the Beach setting for the fishing portal generator.
research-experiment-scanning-fish-second-name = Fish Scanning Experiment 2
research-experiment-scanning-fish-second-desc = An experiment requiring more fish species to be scanned to unlock the Ocean setting for the fishing portal.
research-experiment-scanning-people-android-name = Human Field Research: Full Augmentation
research-experiment-scanning-people-android-desc = Perform a full cybernetic augmentation on a crewmate then scan them to test their newfound capabilities and new sensory and cognitive functions.
research-experiment-scanning-people-augmented-organs-name = Human Field Research: Augmented Organs
research-experiment-scanning-people-augmented-organs-desc = We need to gather data on how cybernetic vital organs integrate with human biology. Conduct a scan on a human with these implants to help us understand their compatibility.
research-experiment-scanning-people-mutant-name = Human Field Research: Genetic Mutations
research-experiment-scanning-people-mutant-desc = Our new research assistants have been drinking random chemicals for science, when one of them mastered telekinesis and another started shooting lasers from the eyes. This could be useful for our studies. Repeat the experiment by making assistants drink unstable mutagen, scan them and report the results.
research-experiment-scanning-people-skillchip-name = Human Field Research: Skill Chip Implants
research-experiment-scanning-people-skillchip-desc = Before sticking programmed circuits into human brain, we need to know how it handles simple ones. Scan a live person with a skill chip implant in their brain.
research-experiment-scanning-points-anomalies-name = Neutralized Anomaly Analysis
research-experiment-scanning-points-anomalies-desc = We have the power to deal with the anomalies now. Neutralize them with an anomaly neutralizer or refine the raw cores in the refinery and scan the results.
research-experiment-scanning-points-bluespace-crystal-name = Bluespace Crystal Sampling
research-experiment-scanning-points-bluespace-crystal-desc = Investigate the properties of bluespace crystals by scanning either an artificial or naturally occurring variant. This will help us deepen our understanding of bluespace phenomena.
research-experiment-scanning-points-machinery-tiered-scan-tier2-any-name = Upgraded Stock Parts Benchmark
research-experiment-scanning-points-machinery-tiered-scan-tier2-any-desc = Our newly-designed machinery components require practical application tests for hints at possible further advancements, as well as a general confirmation that we didnt actually design worse parts somehow. Scan any machinery with Upgraded Parts and report the results.
research-experiment-scanning-points-machinery-tiered-scan-tier3-any-name = Advanced Stock Parts Benchmark
research-experiment-scanning-points-machinery-tiered-scan-tier3-any-desc = Our newly-designed machinery components require practical application tests for hints at possible further advancements, as well as a general confirmation that we didnt actually design worse parts somehow. Scan any machinery with Advanced Parts and report the results.
research-experiment-scanning-points-slime-hard-name = Challenging Slime Survey
research-experiment-scanning-points-slime-hard-desc = Another station has challenged your research team to collect several challenging slime cores, are you up to the task?
research-experiment-scanning-random-janitor-trash-name = Station Hygiene Inspection
research-experiment-scanning-random-janitor-trash-desc = To learn how to clean, we must first learn what it is to have filth. We need you to scan some filth around the station.
research-experiment-scanning-random-mecha-damage-scan-name = Exosuit Materials: Stress Failure Test
research-experiment-scanning-random-mecha-damage-scan-desc = Your exosuit fabricators allow for rapid production on a small scale, but the structural integrity of created parts is inferior to more traditional means.
research-experiment-scanning-random-mecha-equipped-scan-name = Exosuit Materials: Load Strain Test
research-experiment-scanning-random-mecha-equipped-scan-desc = Exosuit equipment places unique strain upon the structure of the vehicle. Scan exosuits you have assembled from your exosuit fabricator and fully equipped to accelerate our structural stress simulations.
research-experiment-scanning-random-plants-traits-name = Unique Biomatter Mutation Sample
research-experiment-scanning-random-plants-traits-desc = We here at CentCom are on the look out for rare and exotic plants with unique properties to brag about to our shareholders. Were looking for a sample with a very specific genes currently.
research-experiment-scanning-random-plants-wild-name = Wild Biomatter Mutation Sample
research-experiment-scanning-random-plants-wild-desc = Due to a number of reasons, (Solar Rays, a diet consisting only of unstable mutagen, entropy) plants with lower levels of instability may occasionally mutate upon harvest. Scan one of these samples for us.
research-experiment-scanning-reagent-cryostylane-name = Pure Cryostylane Scan
research-experiment-scanning-reagent-cryostylane-desc = It appears that the Cryostylane reagent can potentially halt all physiological processes in the human body. Produce Cryostylane at the required purity and scan the beaker.
research-experiment-scanning-reagent-haloperidol-name = Pure Haloperidol Scan
research-experiment-scanning-reagent-haloperidol-desc = We require testing related to the long-term treatment of chronic psychiatric disorders. Produce Haloperidol at the required purity and scan the beaker.
